metadata.name: Sodieum #1
metadata.description: In a small village tucked away in the mountains, there was a legend about a cursed skull that brought misfortune to those who possessed it. The story goes that a group of explorers stumbled upon an ancient temple deep in the heart of the jungle. Inside, they found a large golden skull that seemed to radiate with an otherworldly aura. This is not the end of the story - the story begins here (join us) #Sodieum #SodieumSkulls
